snippet.title: Gori: Cuddly Carnage | Platform Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as a badass murder-kitty on a death-dealing hoverboard in Gori: Cuddly Carnage, a third-person ‘skate ‘n’ slash’ set in a neon-glowing futuristic world filled with intense destruction and fast-paced combat.

Come chat all things Gori, with the devs from Angry Demon Studios over on our Discord:
https://wired.gg/GoriDiscord

Follow all things Gori:
https://twitter.com/GoriCarnage
https://www.facebook.com/GoriCarnage

Developed by Angry Demon Studio, Gori: Cuddle Carnage is available to wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1299690/Gori_Cuddly_Carnage/

Follow Wired: 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/WiredP​​
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WiredPro​​
Discord : https://discord.gg/wiredp​
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/wired_productions/
Wired Unplugged Podcast: https://wired.gg/Unplugged
